===Noun===
'''umat'''

# the [[members]] of a [[community]]
# a [[common]] [[group]] of [[people]]

====Usage notes====
'''Umat''' is usually used in the context of the followers of a religion. <br>
[[ummat|Ummat]] is a spelling variation of [[umat]]

